\end_inset

 is called 
\begin_inset Formula $\textbf{split}$
\end_inset

 when there is an 
\begin_inset Formula $R$
\end_inset

-module isomorphism 
\begin_inset Formula $\theta\colon M\to L\oplus N$
\end_inset

 such that the diagram
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset ERT
