\begin_layout Standard
commutes, where the bottom maps to and from the direct sum are the standard
 embedding and projection; that is
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
\iota_{1}(u)=(u,0)\quad\text{and}\quad\pi_{2}(u,v)=v
\]

\end_inset

for all 
\begin_inset Formula $u\in L$
\end_inset

