\begin_layout Plain Layout


\backslash
begin{defn}
\backslash
label{defn}
\end_layout

\end_inset

 If 
\begin_inset Formula $M\subset E$
\end_inset

 satisfies any of the equivalent properties of 
\begin_inset ERT
